title: Paraquat - Ugly Photo In A Pretty Frame / Painting By Numbers
description:
#1 Ugly Photo In A Pretty Frame
#2 Knives To Cut Holes (People Fall Into)
#3 Painting By Numbers
#4 The Circle Revers

A very special breed of Punk / Hardcore, unlike anything you have ever heard. It was recorded in late 2007 at Blubox Studios in Troisdorf / Germany and released independently on May 16th.

This is the Double-Single taken from their first full-length release "Goodbye Fairground".
